            "text": "The tyrafdir breathes out a noxious mist from all of its mouths, spreading in a 20-foot emanation that deals 4d10 poison damage to creatures within the area (DC 24 basic Reflex save). Any creature that fails its save must attempt a DC 24 Will save or gain weakness to mental 10 and a \u20131 status penalty to Will saves for 24 hours. The tyrafdir can't use Noxious Exhalation again for 1d4 rounds.",
